nodes.text: Jimme Weasle was a male Human residing on Corellia around 3640 BBY, when he was killed.

Jimme Weasle appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Champion boss on Corellia. He is not directly involved in any quests, but can be killed for loot and as part of the achievement. This article assumes 100% game completion, which means he was killed.
